  "text": "Some recent work on matching Web query interfaces [CITATION_1] also exploits the holistic idea. In particular, reference [CITATION_2] explores syntactically similar attributes across multiple interfaces and develops clustering-based matching approaches. Essentially, this work is another realization of local evalua-tion of holistic schema matching by assessing matchings as cluster similarities.",
